title: LET THE GOOD TIMES ROLL! Jazzy urban studio.
posting_body: ["Urban jazzy studio in the heart of St Paul-- just in time for MEARS PARK JAZZ FEST '22!!", 'Catch the bus as it passes your front door!!', " It's time to make a move...", 'Goodbye winter, "hello" Summer!', "Get yourself into this cozy studio with bright views of Downtown St. Paul and Mears Park from your windows'.!", 'This awesome home features lots of natural lighting,  large closets, and plenty of room for your desk-- handy, if you work from home) and open  living spaces.', 'Get a work out in using our 24/7 private Fitness Center and Studio, relax in our indoor heated pool and get toasty warm in our sauna.', 'Mears Park Place is owned and managed by Bigos Management.', 'Conveniently located in trendy Lowertown across from Mears Park, you can walk the skyway down to the river and bike along the Bike trails through the city parks.', 'We are just 2 blocks from Union Depot and the light rail station, which can take you through St. Paul and connects to Minneapolis and the University campus, as well as the airport.', 'Mears Park Place Apartments features:', '* Indoor Pool', '* Sun Patio', '*', 'Rec Room', '* Sauna', '* Tanning Bed', '* Party Room', '* 24hr gym with fitness studio', '* Underground Parking', 'Call', 'show contact info', 'to schedule your self-guided tour today!', '(Tell them you saw #530 on Craigslist!)', '*Pricing and availability are both determined by requested move-in date, cannot be guaranteed due to on-site leasing activity, and are subject to change at any time.']
